      "writtenOn": "2026-05-28T16:07:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m a little confused how this works....  If you\u0027re registering this in the normal table, isn\u0027t it just doing a blocking call still?\n\nWhen you write your example, maybe include a timer in the callback to show that it\u0027s working the way we expect it to.",
